th\u0103m con g\u00e1i \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee3 c\u0169. Tuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u00e0. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 khi Shovkovskiy ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 c\u0169. Anh c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c b\u00e0 Lyubov Pavlovna v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng tr\u00ean l\u1ea7u v\u00e0 mang ra m\u1ed9t kh\u1ea9u s\u00fang l\u1ee5c.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/cc-6392-1523330424.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau khi g\u00f5 c\u1eeda, Shovkovskiy quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i xe, n\u01a1i v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng camera \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i. Shovkovskiy v\u00e0 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 Olga Alenova ly d\u1ecb t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10/2015.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"Lyubov Pavlovna nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i v\u00e0 n\u00e9m nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 ba ta l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb ban c\u00f4ng. B\u00e0 ta b\u1eafn ba ph\u00e1t s\u00fang nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m ch\u1ea1y ra kh\u1ecfi nh\u00e0 sau khi nghe ti\u1ebfng s\u00fang\", c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Dynamo Kiev cho bi\u1ebft. Shovkovskiy c\u0169ng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 c\u0169 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb k\u1ebft t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7n r\u01b0\u1ee3u v\u00e0 b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00e1u g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a b\u00e0. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 con g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a anh.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nShovkovskiy c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p s\u00e2n c\u1ecf k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 23 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 th\u00e1ng 12/2016 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 41.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1000","checkdouble":"183934"},{"date":"14:34 10/04","title":"Doanh thu c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf Puma theo Adidas","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/8/doanh-thu-cua-arsenal-hua-hen-tang-manh-neu-bo-puma-theo-adidas.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-dec