7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CLB Ha Noi mat Dinh Trong o vong 5 V-League - Tin bong da 24h hinh anh\" title=\"CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/CLB-Ha-Noi-mat-Dinh-Trong-o-vong-5-V-League---Tin-bong-da-24h-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB\u00a0</em><i>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. V\u00e0 anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n H\u00f2a Xu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a V-League.\u00a0C\u00f2n Duy M\u1ea1nh th\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c em c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay kh\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M\u1ea1nh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u1ea3 quan h\u01a1n\u201d, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam n\u00f3i v\u1edbi B\u00e1o B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ngay trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL v\u1eeba qua. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay cho anh l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC b\u1edfi HAGL khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecdc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Anh t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u2018chuy\u00ean gia b\u1eaft T\u00e2y\u2019 t\u1ea1i V-League. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u00e0y sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c\u00a0H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 5 V-League c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng V\u0103n H\u1eadu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"992","checkdouble":"183952"},{"date":"14:50 10/04","title":"Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/klopp-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro-truoc-dai-chien-voi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-w