ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u01a1n cu\u1ed3ng n\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League \u0111\u00eam nay n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohamed Salah, Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain v\u00e0 Sadio Mane l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n cho Liverpool trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ea1i Anfield. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u0103ng hoa trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1eb1ng 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a The Citizens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n trong hi\u1ec7p hai khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u00ecnh r\u1eadp ch\u1edd ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng khi n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch qu\u00fd gi\u00e1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp canh bao cac cau thu Liverpool truoc dai chien voi Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/Klopp-canh-bao-cac-cau-thu-Liverpool-truoc-dai-chien-voi-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV&nbsp;Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-liverpool-vs-man-city-01h45-ngay-54-champions-league-201718-372-183531.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City b\u1ecb v\u00f9i d\u1eadp t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1</span> nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia ph\u00e2n t\u00edch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng The Citizens v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Anfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Klopp m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 quan v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn derby Manchester cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Man City gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n b\u00e3o l\u1ed1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</em><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\">Man City vs Liverpool (1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4): C\u00f2n n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n t\u00e1t</span><br>\r\n<span>B\u01b0\u1edbc ra th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba Etihad cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn sinh t\u1eed Man City vs Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd m\u00f4ng lung kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u n\u00e0o hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p hai, h\u1ecd thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. V\u00e0 sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pogba, Man United l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong khi Man City l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb l\u1ea1c nh\u1ecbp. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 theo ki\u1ec3u n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo c\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. C\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1eady th\u00f4i. D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 m\u1edbi mong l\u1ecdt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League n\u0103m nay&rdquo;</em>, HLV&nbsp;Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City vs Liverpool:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/pep-man-city-phai-co-tran-dau-hoan-hao-truoc-liverpool-184-183923.html\">Pep ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Man City v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/van-dijk-khong-ngu-duoc-sau-tran-thang-man-city-184-183930.html\">Van Dijk kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\">Man City vs Liverpool (1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4): C\u00f2n n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n t\u00e1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/salah-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-man-city-184-183907.html\">Super Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-liverpool-lo-so-ky-tich-nguoc-dong-cua-man-city-184-183899.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Liverpool lo s\u1ee3 k\u1ef3 t\u00edch ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/trent-alexanderarnold-chia-khoa-bao-toan-chien-thang-cho-liverpool-392-183886.html\">Trent Alexander-Arnold: Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></ht