6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Valverde e ng\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dzeko b\u00ean ph\u00eda AS Roma, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League n\u0103m nay.</h2>\r\n<h2>Barca \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc AS Roma \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. 2 b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a De Rossi v\u00e0 Kostas Manolas \u0111\u01b0a g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2-0. V\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, Barca ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Gerard Pique ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c Roma ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd g\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat 80 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Edin Dzeko. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5 s\u00fang \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u1edf ph\u00fat 87. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a Suarez \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AS Roma cua Dzeko\" title=\"AS Roma cua Dzeko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/day-chien-thuat-roma-vs-barca-tu-ket-c1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV&nbsp;Valverde e ng\u1ea1i Dzeko c\u1ee7a Roma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 quan l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i Olimpico di\u1ec5n ra, HLV Valverde cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Edin Dzeko cho th\u1ea5y Roma v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o nguy hi\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Roma ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai. B\u1edfi v\u00ec khi b\u1ea1n \u1edf trong th\u1ebf b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i, \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00f4i tin \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Roma \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-vs-barca-1h45-ngay-114-no-nan-chong-chat-184-183919.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/roma-vs-barca-1h45-ngay-114-no-nan-chong-chat.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-vs-barca-1h45-ngay-114-no-nan-chong-chat-184-183919.html\">Roma vs Barca (1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4): N\u1ee3 n\u1ea7n ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\n<span>AS Roma v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng san l\u1ea5p kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch thua Barcelona 1-4 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Champions League, ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng Roma c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Roma. S\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Dzeko l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng&quot;, </em>HLV&nbsp;Valverde l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 e ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dzeko<em>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi n\u00f3i c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m b\u1edfi n\u00f3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ef1 tin qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-vs-barca-1h45-ngay-114-no-nan-chong-chat-184-183919.html\">Roma vs Barca (1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4): N\u1ee3 n\u1ea7n ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-don-tin-vui-truoc-them-tu-ket-luot-ve-champions-league-184-183824.html\">Barca \u0111\u00f3n tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-barca-41-roma-184-183670.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Barca 4-1 Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-chi-thang-vi-duoc-trong-tai-giup-suc-184-183564.html\">Barca ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-tro-barca-len-mat-thang-nho-phan-luoi-thi-sao-chu-184-183552.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca l\u00ean m\u1eb7t: Th\u1eafng nh\u1edd ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi, th\u00ec sao ch\u1ee9?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-barca-41-roma-184-183550.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Barca 4-1 Roma</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"989","checkdouble":"183942"},{"date":"16:31 10/04","title":"Lampard: \"Man City v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/10/lampard-man-city-van-con-co-ho