t. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man City l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea &ndash; Frank Lampard nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Liverpool \u0111ang n\u1eafm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ai \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ng\u00e3 ng\u0169. N\u1ebfu Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1-2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. B\u1edfi khi Liverpool c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ghi 5 b\u00e0n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u1eddi gian b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Man City. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, khi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ng\u00e3 ng\u0169\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/lampard-man-city-van-con-co-hoi-truoc-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u Man City vs Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ng\u00e3 ng\u0169</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, n\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch Man City vs Liverpool x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1c \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Frank Lampard c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua tai h\u1ea1i MU cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn Man City. Anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;V\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn derby Manchester, b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Man City m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta mong \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c MU 4 ho\u1eb7c 5 b\u00e0n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft, n\u1ebfu Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd&hellip; c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t Liverpool trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 PSG \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca, sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/pep-man-city-phai-co-tran-dau-hoan-hao-truoc-liverpool-184-183923.html\">Pep ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Man City v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/klopp-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro-truoc-dai-chien-voi-man-city-184-183920.html\">Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat-184-183914.html\">Man City vs Liverpool (1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4): C\u00f2n n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n t\u00e1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/salah-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-man-city-184-183907.html\">Super Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/klopp-man-city-dang-ra-phai-thang-mu-den-60-184-183906.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;Man City \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng MU \u0111\u1ebfn 6-0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/sao-man-city-to-liverpool-su-dung-chien-thuat-tieu-cuc-184-183905.html\">Sao Man City t\u1ed1 Liverpool s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">