g\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean d\u1ef1a theo nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nCeballos c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ee5i t\u00e0n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Betis 2 m\u00f9a qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/sao-tre-dani-ceballos-o-lai-real-madrid-180-182932.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dani Ceballos</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Sau c\u00f9ng, anh ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 18 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Madrid l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Ceballos. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4i qua g\u1ea7n h\u1ebft song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 16 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Real bao g\u1ed3m 11 trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid ban Dani Ceballos cho Liverpool he 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n Dani Ceballos cho Liverpool h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/real-madrid-ban-dani-ceballos-cho-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ceballos \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, nghe \u0111\u00e2u ch\u00ednh Ceballos \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t m\u00e3n v\u1edbi HLV Zinedine Zidane. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, anh c\u00f2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ng\u00f3 l\u01a1 nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian qua.</div>\r\n<h2>Real mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Ceballos cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThay v\u00ec l\u1eafng nghe Dani Ceballos, c\u00e1c s\u1ebfp Real c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB, Zidane. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Betis v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 2 (9 ph\u00fat \u00edt \u1ecfi). L\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ceballos \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Don Balon m\u1edbi mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin: K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch Real Madrid b\u00e1n Dani Ceballos cho Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch huy \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n kinh ph\u00ed l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Los Blancos n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Vi\u1ec7c chia tay Ceballos c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"perez\" title=\"perez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/3/Sao-Bayern-tha-thinh-thanh-cong-2-dai-gia-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez mu\u1ed1n Real Madrid b\u00e1n Dani Ceballos cho Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Real v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Dani Ceballos trong th\u1eddi gian qua \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 t\u1eeb Liverpool. Vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-chuan-bi-day-sao-tre-sang-liverpool-180-181000.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool mua Ceballos</strong></span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thay th\u1ebf Emre Can s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real th\u1eeba bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111ang s\u1eb5n ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Philippe Coutinho cho Barcelone (thu v\u1ec1 160 tri\u1ec7u Euro). \u0110\u00f4i b\u00ean s\u1ebd s\u1edbm c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi ti\u1ebft trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-va-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-183921.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U v\u00e0 