zard van lac quan hinh anh\" title=\"Chelsea kh\u00f3 v\u00e0o top 4, Hazard v\u1eabn l\u1ea1c quan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Chelsea-kho-vao-top-4,-Hazard-van-lac-quan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f3 v\u00e0o top 4 sau khi b\u1ecb West Ham c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-chelsea-vs-west-ham-22h30-ngay-84-premier-league-201718-372-183811.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb West Ham c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</span> ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n. C\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 v\u1eadn may \u0111ang l\u1ea9n tr\u00e1nh Conte v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Tottenham b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau v\u00f2ng 33. V\u00e0 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa l\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch tr\u1eddi bi\u1ec3n v\u1edbi Spurs.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n sa th\u1ea3i Conte nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span><br>\r\n<span>BL\u0110 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdp g\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Conte. Theo Daily Mail, Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 C1 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 si\u00eau sao Eden Hazard. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng Champions League v\u00e0o n\u0103m sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng FA Cup \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi b\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Chelsea, b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. Nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. V\u1eady n\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i khi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 Champions League c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed1t. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 Champions League b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-sa-thai-conte-nhung-lai-tu-choi-den-bu-9-trieu-bang-172-183929.html\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n sa th\u1ea3i Conte nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-alvaro-morata-cua-chelsea-172-183915.html\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/batshuayi-lai-xat-muoi-noi-dau-cua-chelsea-172-183903.html\">Batshuayi l\u1ea1i x\u00e1t mu\u1ed1i n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/conte-buon-buc-vi-bi-ban-than-tru-eo-tuong-lai-o-chelsea-172-183897.html\">Conte bu\u1ed3n b\u1ef1c v\u00ec b\u1ecb b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n tr\u00f9 \u1ebbo t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/watford-chot-gia-ban-hang-hot-richarlison-172-183879.html\">Watford ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng hot Richarlison</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><s