color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, Man United \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. Nh\u01b0ng Jose Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Sanchez c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 2 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf - th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i trong hi\u1ec7p 1, v\u00e0 b\u1eebng t\u1ec9nh trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Gi\u1eefa 2 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 10 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u1edf n\u1eeda sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo trung v\u1ec7 Chris Smalling ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-da-noi-gi-de-giup-mu-nguoc-dong-kinh-dien-truoc-man-city-172-183768.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u0169 h\u1ec1 nh\u00ecn Man xanh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span>. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t chia s\u1ebb. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cTrong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 b\u1ecb \u00e9p s\u00e2n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho noi ve Sanchez nhung gi trong tran derby hinh anh\" title=\"Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Sanchez nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trong tr\u1eadn derby h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/mourinho-da-noi-gi-de-sanchez-lot-xac-tran-derby.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c trong hi\u1ec7p 2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City. Paul Pogba, Ander Herrera v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea7n h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\u201d \u2013 HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. \u201cH\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 tin thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00f9i Man City v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i k\u00e9m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7p 1.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u00e2ng cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7\u201d \u2013 Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 10 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u1ea1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Paul Pogba l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, v\u00e0 Chris Smalling \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 3-2 cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Alexis Sanchez c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, khi c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Sanchez v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a MU ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Man xanh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265774\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/04/08/highlight-man-city-vs-man-utd-vong-33-nha.mp4&autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Alexis Sanchez tr\u00ean bongda24h<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-cau-tra-loi-cua-alexis-sanchez-172-183870.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/du-am-man-city-23-mu-cau-tra-loi-cua-alexis-sanchez.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-man-city-23-mu-cau-tra-loi-cua-alexis-sanchez-172-183870.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Man City 2-3 MU: C\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u201c\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ee5t\u201d c\u1ee7a Sanchez, v\u1edbi CLB hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 Man City vs MU 2-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby-172-183865.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sanchez-noi-gi-voi-pogba-truoc-tran-derby-172-183865.html\">Sanchez n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn derby?</span><br>\r\nTrong cu\u1e