ont-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 John Stones, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>John Stones kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 John Stones kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-3 c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hoc tro khong hai long, Pep Guardiola phat bieu ve John Stones hinh anh\" title=\"H\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 John Stones h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/Hoc-tro-khong-hai-long,-Pep-Guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-John-Stones-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>John Stones th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Italia, Stones ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/man-city-1471.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City</strong></span>. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 John Stones, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. B\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/john-stones-thua-nhan-dang-gap-kho-khan-o-man-city-172-182830.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>John Stones kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</strong></span> v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pep ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do Stones kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Stones, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Otamendi v\u00e0 Stones l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola phat bieu ve John Stones\" title=\"Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 John Stones\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/pep-giai-thich-ly-do-loai-bo-john-stones.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 John Stones</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn Stones g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a Stones tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu anh c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, Stones kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Laporte hay Otamendi, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. N\u1ebfu <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/john-stones-53464.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Stones</strong></span> ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a John Stone \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/152077-40942/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a John Stone \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"984","checkdouble":"183941"},{"date":"16:30 10/04","title":"B\u1ecb Conte lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Christensen v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/bi-conte-loai-bo-christensen-van-len-tieng-cam-on.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-