r-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Andreas Christensen ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte, anh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u00ecnh.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Christensen b\u1ecb Conte tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Andreas Christensen \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Gary Cahill, Antonio Rudiger v\u00e0 Cesar Azpilicueta \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andreas Christensen phat bieu ve Antonio Conte hinh anh\" title=\"Andreas Christensen ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Andreas-Christensen-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Christensen b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t sau nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. Theo \u0111\u00f3, trong tr\u1eadn thua Tottenham 1-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cham-diem-chelsea-13-tottenham-172-183344.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Christensen&nbsp;m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp</strong></span> \u1edf 2/3 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/andreas-christensen-54231.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Christensen</strong></span> c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u1edbi Barca \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, d\u00f9 HLV Conte li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u00ean v\u1ef1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u00ec \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Christensen v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Conte</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-1 West Ham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 o\u00e1n tr\u00e1ch \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andreas Christensen ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte, anh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi Conte loai bo Christensen van len tieng cam on hinh anh 2\" title=\"B\u1ecb Conte lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Christensen v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/bi-conte-loai-bo-christensen-van-len-tieng-cam-on.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andreas Christensen ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i 25 \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m n\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Conte, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong thi \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChristensen n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Conte, anh h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi: &ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Andreas Christensen \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/186795-40942/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Andreas Christensen \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"983","checkdouble":"183943"},{"date":"16:53 10/04","title":"V\u00ec sao Marcus Rashford kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean r\u1eddi MU?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/10/vi-sao-marcus-rashford-khong-nen-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.m