00ednh x\u00e1c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Alexis Sanchez c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho sao tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt nay c\u00f2n \u00edt h\u01a1n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn derby Manchester m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng, khi anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u00edt ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, khi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u00e1c tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Marcus Rashford r\u1eddi MU \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-mua-rashford-sao-tre-bi-that-sung-cua-mu-180-182693.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid nh\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0a Rashford v\u1ec1 Bernabeu</span> v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford r\u1eddi MU l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra\" title=\"Rashford r\u1eddi MU l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/vi-sao-marcus-rashford-khong-nen-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rashford r\u1eddi MU l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n MU l\u00e0 Danny Higginbotham (\u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7) cho r\u1eb1ng, Rashford n\u00ean ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn t\u00ecm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf Old Trafford. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed5i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i Man United.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u1edf trong m\u1ed9t CLB ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5y ai \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m v\u00ed d\u1ee5, h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Jesse Lingard, m\u1ed9t minh ch\u1ee9ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Lingard n\u0103m nay 25 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man United.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Rashford c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean&rdquo; &ndash; Danny Higginbotham chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jose Mourinho tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, ch\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-vs-liverpool-rashford-va-lukaku-giup-mourinho-mo-mat-172-181754.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rashford \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Liverpool 2-1</span>. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Rashford r\u1eddi MU l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tin t\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 MU tr\u00ean bongda24h<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/mu-treo-anh-messi-lau-giay-de-giao-duc-lua-tre-188-183936.html\">MU treo \u1ea3nh Messi lau gi\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ashley-young-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-mu-nguoc-dong-truoc-man-city-172-183922.html\">Ashley Young ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap M.U ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/klopp-man-city-dang-ra-phai-thang-mu-den-60-184-183906.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;Man City \u0111\u00e1ng ra ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng MU \u0111\u1ebfn 6-0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/toa-sang-o-derby-manchester-pogba-van-that-vong-tran-tre-172-183889.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf derby Manchester, v\u00ec sao Pogba v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/nghi-an-sao-mu-co-tinh-khac-nho-vao-logo-cua-man-city-188-183883.html\">Nghi \u00e1n sao MU c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u1ea1c nh\u1ed5 v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tiet-lo-bat-ngo-ve-nguoi-hung-cua-mu-trong-tran-derby-172-183877.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a MU trong tr\u1eadn derby</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"982","checkdouble":"183946"},{"date":"12:17 10/04","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U v\u00e0 Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-va-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-si