2>\r\n<h2>Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lazio, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU va Real theo duoi, Milinkovic-Savic phat bieu ve tuong lai hinh anh\" title=\"MU v\u00e0 Real theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/MU-va-Real-theo-duoi,-Milinkovic-Savic-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-hang-hot-serie-a-172-174713.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U quan t\u00e2m Milinkovic-Savic</strong></span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia thay Carrick. Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford chi ra 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-co-doi-thu-lon-trong-thuong-vu-sergej-milinkovicsavic-172-180903.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic</strong></span>, Los Blancos c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay Luka Modric, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Milinkovic-Savic l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 r\u1eddi Lazio hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y: \u201cB\u00e1o ch\u00ed n\u00f3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. T\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Lazio c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"MU mua Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-293-mu-mua-pogba-moi-voi-gia-ngang-pogba-xin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap Lazio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Lazio, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi xem x\u00e9t nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, Mateja Kezman th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Pogba, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho M.U.\u00a0T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng Pogba, nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTrong 6 th\u00e1ng qua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Lazio, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/356160-42720/033100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"981","checkdouble":"183921"}]}